node.text:
How are we feeling the growing trend of unique glass stairscases? Yay or Nay? I'm guilty of this interior pleasure and design! Glass stairs are truly stunning architectural features that can create breathtaking visuals. A set of stairs made entirely of glass can make those climbing the steps appear as if they’re treading on air. However, some fear it. The huge variety of shapes and sizes, along with the range of complementary materials that can be integrated, mean that the design options for glass-stair systems are virtually limitless.
.

Do you like open-concept homes 🧡? ⁣
⁣
A home is full of corners to enjoy the best moments of the day with your family. This effortlessly beautiful open-concept home of @liebevolles.zuhause⁣ features interconnected spaces without barriers, allowing people to flow from one room to the next without feeling disconnected 🖐🏻🙂. ⁣

SWIPE 👉🏻 to the end to see how cozy this bathroom 🚿 is in the evening! The bathroom is typically the smallest room, but it doesn’t necessarily mean that it shouldn’t be as cozy or illuminated as the other rooms of your home. This #Nordic bathroom of @frk_furu ⁣is both cozy during the day 🌞 and night 🌓. The lighting in this bathroom is both functional and relaxing. Even the 🐶 loves it! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
As the number of light sources helps to create an atmosphere, the possibilities are endless. As can be seen, adding candles is a creative idea to instantly transform your bathroom or any other parts of your home into a cozy retreat. Most Scandinavian bathrooms like this have similar styles such as clean lines, neutral colours, practical concepts that maximize space and function, elegance highlighted by natural materials and lots of light ✨. ⁣

SWIPE 👉🏻 for a creative space-saving method for your closet. Inspiration by @isii_bla. ⁣
⁣
Do you know that 𝐁𝐮𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐨 𝐫𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐠 a shirt is a great way to save space in your drawers or closet? This is especially useful if the shirt bears a logo or design that will help you spot it in the drawer. Not only will you fit more tees in the drawer, but you’ll also find the shirt you want in no time at all. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣ ⁣⁣
👕 Benefits of rolling your shirts 👕⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
(1) Your clothes will have fewer creases ✔︎⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
(2) You can easily find what you need ✔︎⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
(3) You can store a lot more in your drawers, depending on how you organize them ✔︎⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
